	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas accepi, chare frater, una cum consignatione historiae vel actorum... Gaudeo autem coetum hunc tandem dissolutum esse, atque utinam feliciter dissolutus sit et nihil sequatur tristius!</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habemus in <placeName ref="l862" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Helvetia</placeName> fel omnia amaricans; dominus expurgare dignetur bilem hanc cum patriae salute!</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Intelligis me loqui de illis, de quibus <persName ref="p20020" cert="high">Abdias</persName> propheta vaticinatur, nisi <persName type="auto_name">Moabitas</persName> malis etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratias tibi ago pro illis tuis laboribus; vix legere datur, quod tu tanta facilitate scribis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nuper arbitror me tibi de incendio nostro scripsisse, quo tectum turris templi nostri conflagravit maximo omnium nostrum cum periculo, rursus maxima cum dei gratia et defensione.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si historiam non misi, mittam alias, si monueris; puto tamen me tibi summam exposuisse rei.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Oremus dominum, ut portenta haec non sint ostenta maiorum malorum; quae si a domino inferrentur, accusari non posset; tanta est omnium per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiam</placeName> consceleratio.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich fürcht, ich fürcht, es sye nitt wyt vom end und von der vergälltung.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Antverpia</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l210" cert="high">Heydelberga</placeName> scribitur exules <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20" cert="high">Belgas</placeName> occupasse insulam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20" cert="high">Hollandiae</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name">Bryel</placeName> et totam prope <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2012">Selandiam</placeName>; habere illos auxilia ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Dania</placeName> et, ut quidam suspicantur, ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName>, sub praetextu tamen <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20180" cert="high">Ludovici a Nassow</persName>; certe signa <persName type="auto_name">Aurantii</persName> in vexillis ostendere dicuntur.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p6789" cert="high">Albanus</persName> contra militem colligit et satagit.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid futurum sit, novit dominus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> scribitur imperatorem <persName type="auto_name">Turcarum</persName> fatis concessisse eique surrogatum filium eius, principem prudentem et moderatum necnon et bellicosissimum.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> habemus pacem servari inviolatam et ecclesias crescere.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Jetzund ist by mir ein burger von <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> gesin, der dem brieff und gällt <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3082">Stupani</persName> nachfraget, und wie ich geantwort, das ichs frommklich hinabgeschikt, hab ich imm erst darzuͦ verzeichnen und schryben muͤssen, wie es gangen, alls ob ich sunst nüt zuͦ thuͦn habe.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Hat mich gebätten, üch zuͦ schriben, das ir neißwan einem, der üch den brieff und gällt zuͦgesandt, embieten söllind, er frage flissig nahin und wölle, das er imm empfolhen, trüwlich nachkummen etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus tecum et cum universa tua familia.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> postera ascensionis domini 1572.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta dominos et amicos nostros ordine omnes.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eximio Christi ministro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Thobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae pastori, fratri meo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An h. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Thobiam Egli</persName>, pfarrer zuͦ S. Martin zuͦ <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
